The gender neutral restroom is about 20 feet to the right of the lab check in window. The restroom is very large and has a toilet and urinal, with plenty of space for someone in a wheelchair and a caregiver.

name: First Universalist Church of Auburn
street: 169 Pleasant St  (and the office, 159 Pleasant St, side door)
directions: The church is open on Sundays from about 9 to noon (service at 10 if you're interested!)  The church office is open MWF 9:30-1:30 except federal holidays and Auburn School Dept. snow days. If the door is locked during those hours, just ring the doorbell -- you are welcome here.

name: New Vic Theatre

comment: All toilets are safe for transgendered people to use, the New Vic has a written inclusiveness policy specifically including trans people. Any harassment should be reported to a member of staff who will be happy to support you. All toilets are available for the general public to use, so you won't need to pretend to be a customer!
